To pick up the trail, Jesse needs to get inside his own head for a one-on-one talk with his guest - and for that, a fistful of peyote taken under the open Arizona sky seems just the ticket. What's waiting for him in Monument Valley, however, is something much less spiritual: an entire U.S. Army tank regiment, commandeered by the newly elevated Allfather of the Grail, Herr Starr.
